text: Munster Technological University () or MTU is a technological university (TU). It is in Cork and Tralee in Ireland. It was opened on 1 January 2021. Both institutes of technology, Cork Institute of Technology and IT Tralee were merged to make MTU. ==References== Category:21st-century establishments in the Republic of Ireland Category:2021 establishments in Europe Category:Technical colleges and universities in Europe Category:Colleges and universities in Ireland
title: Munster Technological University
